Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:18.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:24.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:29.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:36.68,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:41.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:48.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:52.56,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:57.73,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:06.24,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:12.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:17.25,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:23.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.69,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(109,138)}MISS MACROSS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:52.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:52.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:53.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:57.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's up? Why'd you ask me\Nout here all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:00.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I just thought I'd ask you\Nto a movie or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. It's almost rush time\Nat the restaurant. I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:09.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I forgot. I've been\Nlosing track of time lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:11.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a sky up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?\NBut some military people made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:19.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mornings and evenings, they'll project a sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, isn't that a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, don't you think it's great?\NWe can see a beautiful twilight every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:27.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Twilight...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe nobody even wants to go\Nback to Earth anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, they're even going\Nto start broadcasting TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:55.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! Did you know Jamis Merin\Nis entering the Miss Macross contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:58.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Jamis Merin is aboard the Macross?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:02.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, she probably came for the launch\Nceremony. The real Jamis Merin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go? It's this Saturday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:10.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't think Saturday's gonna work.\NI'm on duty all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, military life is rough even for a 2nd Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:13.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Irish coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:14.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Yes, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:17.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll bring you some dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but maybe regular\Npeople can't get in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How many should I cook for, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:28.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, for two is okay. It'll just be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:35.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear Minmay's gonna enter\Nthe Miss Macross contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:39.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To celebrate the launch of MBS,\Nthe Macross Broadcast System,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we present the Miss Macross Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-eight beautiful contestants\Nwill take to the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,having been selected from a total\Nof four hundred applicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:57.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will make it to the finals and win the crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss Macross Contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:02.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our queen will be chosen by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay is going to enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you wanna go watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Leader said I could have Saturday off.\NAnd you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:14.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he could handle it alone?\NHe was in a really good mood, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so it's springtime\Nfor our Leader, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean he's got a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:29.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Miss Macross?\NWhat are you entering that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:32.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To celebrate the launch of MBS,\Nthe Macross Broadcast System,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we present the Miss Macross Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayor sent in my application\Nwithout telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-eight beautiful contestants\Nwill take to the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:42.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,having been selected from a total\Nof four hundred applicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:46.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will make it to the finals and win the crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I just think it's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss Macross Contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:57.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our queen will be chosen by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that communications\Non a rather large scale
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,are being broadcast inside the enemy battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we tap into them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:13.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They are medium-wave transmissions\Ncontaining very little information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:27.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:30.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, sir.\NIt began only fifteen {\i1}mikra{\i0} ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, prepare a recon craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:40.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Engines 1 and 2 climbing from 24 to 36.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:53.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the flagship-based\N8th Force Recon Battalion, 099.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Crew: three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission: to intercept and record the\Nenemy ship's internal communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our codename: Blue Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:37.28,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, thank you\Nall for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.41,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss Macross Contest,\Nthe first broadcast of MBS,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.44,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,the Macross Broadcast System,\Nis about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:49.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds to air!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:51.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.36,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrating the launch of MBS,\Nthe Macross Broadcast System,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:00.89,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,this is the Miss Macross Contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:40.21,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the twenty-eight beauties standing\Non this stage today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:45.17,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,only one can have the honor of\Nbeing chosen as Miss Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:48.74,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,And that lucky lady will win a fabulous prize:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.52,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fanliner, the latest model in sports jets,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.62,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,which has been equipped with\Na VA hydro-turbine engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:59.62,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,This model is based on a design by lkki Takemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.36,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one lady is suited to own\Nsuch a high-class machine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.16,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,and that lady is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That really is something else, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:10.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's brand-new. That it was\Nassembled right here on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:14.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, allow me to introduce our judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:20.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,First up, there's the captain of the\NMacross, Commodore Global!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:24.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, the Captain\Nlooks pretty dignified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a dirty look in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:28.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you should have entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You might have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy craft has begun circling\Nus at 12 o'clock high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a recon ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's on standby right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion Team, commanded by...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:47.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lieutenant Hikaru Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prometheus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Call up 2nd Lt. Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He's not there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:24.08,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry number 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.91,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Shoh Blackstone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.08,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Blackstone is a college student\Nwho will turn twenty this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.60,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,and she says her likes\Ninclude apple pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I got them to have you come out last.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jamis Merin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought that they'd\Nhave you come out first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was their way of being\N"accommodating"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! It's always, always like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! This isn't Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you bothering with something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Miss Jamis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:05.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get your autograph? I'm a big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:09.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but this is all I have right now.\NCould you sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm not feeling well right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:18.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want an autograph, you should\Nbring a proper autograph book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:23.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 12, Lynn Minmay!\NPlease get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:30.61,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry number 12, Miss Lynn Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:38.62,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Lynn Minmay was visiting from Yokohama\Nwhen she got caught up in the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Chinese dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:49.59,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,This cute young girl just turned\Nsixteen last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:57.47,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Judges, feel free to ask your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:11:01.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're much prettier in person\Nthan in your photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:02.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I still don't have anyone\NI could call a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have a lot of friends though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Friends"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:12.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you're an only child.\NIs it hard for you to get close to boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:17.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I have a cousin who's like\Na big brother to me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A cousin who's like a big brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:21.16,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lieutenant Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.30,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lieutenant Hikaru Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:30.76,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're there, please contact\Nthe bridge immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do THEY want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bridge, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:50.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU! What kind of a soldier wanders off\Nwhen he's on standby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy vessel is right on top of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:52.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:56.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get back to the Prometheus,\Nand hurry! This is a scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...GET IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:09.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell? If it's a scramble,\Nthey should launch everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:21.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Prometheus, and step on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:30.23,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry number 13, Miss Hiromi Rockfield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Vermillion 1. I have just launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lieutenant Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:21.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That armored loadout is only\Nauthorized for special missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:26.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't launch the Ghosts\Neither, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you make such\Ndecisions on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just provide\Nsupport for the Ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, could you just give me\Nthe enemy's position?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like our military transmissions\Nare being jammed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...might not get to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:49.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The store that kinda has a lot:\NGeneral Products, located in the third ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we move on to round two\Nof the judging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:59.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the swimsuit competition, where\Nthe contestants' bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:01.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Switch to channel D-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:01.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:11.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Radio guidance is useless, so we're\Nswitching to laser guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish is my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Are we getting anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's coming in with no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just started recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, patch the visuals up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Should they be doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:36.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There are men and women\Naboard the same ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:46.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem tense. Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting some static here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it bad on your end too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:53.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like switching to D-3 didn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:14:59.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:04.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:15.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry number 10, Miss Mickley Forrester!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Just two more before my Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew that Minmay had such a cute body?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's compact but she\Ncomes fully equipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 12!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:31.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please head to the stage entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:33.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:38.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry number 12, Miss Lynn Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:38.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:44.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they testing combat suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:48.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think a flimsy uniform like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be much use in combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:53.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:56.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't put it into words,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:59.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel a kind of excitement that's different\Nfrom what I get during combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:02.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm definitely getting a strange,\Ntingly kind of feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,that's making my chest pound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:07.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when you win a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:11.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's more like a shock.\NI'm definitely feeling quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How many are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One unit! It's the one from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This just isn't my day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:34.94,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry number 28, Miss Jamis Merin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:49.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, could you give us a famous\Nline from one of your movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'd like to dance, but I just can't."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:56.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"So please... Could you move your foot?\NYou're standing on my dress."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:15.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still recording that information, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm getting everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Plow through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:45.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:54.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Checking for damage.\NWe're configured for attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:06.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:13.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:16.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:27.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! Get to the escape capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Blue Wind. Our recon craft\Nhas been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have also destroyed an enemy fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we've failed to retrieve any data.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction of enemy recon\Ncraft confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lift the air-raid alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's watch the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:35.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the final round of judging!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will have the honor of being\Ncrowned Miss Macross?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:43.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! They're already down to the finalists!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we've missed most of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:49.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's keeping that patrol unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:51.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably checking out all the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:53.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look! Jamis Merin is still there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid, of course she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:04.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than Jamis, there really aren't\Nany girls left who make an impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:08.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That girl from the Nyan-Nyan\Nrestaurant is one of the finalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:10.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was all over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:13.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I'm in a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! At this rate, things are\Nlooking pretty good for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:18.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet! Miss Macross, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:19.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}She doesn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:24.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right from the start, this contest was just a\Npopularity stunt for Jamis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:26.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be famous, but it's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:30.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A famous actress like her should have\Nbeen made a guest judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:34.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So if she's actually competing, it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:37.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... It's been rigged\Nso that she'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Everyone here in the audience\Ndecides the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:49.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our seven judges have chosen these\Nfive beauties as our finalists!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:52.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the members of the audience\Nwill cast their votes to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:56.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,which of these young ladies will\Nbe crowned Miss Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:59.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've all chosen wisely, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:03.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, it's time for the voting section\Nof our Miss Macross contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.47,0:22:06.25,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, please take hold\Nof the switch by your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:09.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When I give the signal, press the switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:11.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:14.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Swtich on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:25.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a winner! It's been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:26.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Macross is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:28.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lynn Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:38.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it, everyone!\NOur Minmay is Miss Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:53.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.73,0:22:56.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,MBS, the Macross Broadcast System,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:22:59.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,celebrates its launch by bringing you\Nthe Miss Macross contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:04.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And Miss Lynn Minmay has been crowned\Nour queen! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:07.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Minmay's the queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:14.10,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Minmay's dreams has come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:19.65,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,But to Hikaru, it was a very sad event.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:23.88,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,For as Minmay gazed off far into the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:28.84,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru saw a world that\Nhe knew he could never enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:35.06,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(82,111)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:35.06,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,459)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:41.93,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,An intimidation attack by the Zentradi fleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.93,0:23:45.43,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,renders the Macross's radar system inoperable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:49.19,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of this, Misa boards\Na Cat's Eye recon plane and,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:53.11,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,with Hikaru's team providing guard,\Nfollows behind the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:56.93,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:01.72,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(98,144)}BLIND GAME
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:23:58.87,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"BLIND GAME"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.08,0:24:23.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.28,0:24:29.68,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.95,0:24:36.25,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.56,0:24:44.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.30,0:24:50.67,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.97,0:24:56.53,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.84,0:25:04.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.38,0:25:15.62,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
